      BCUHRSUIUJGUOCABDEUKFTGUSABCEFULDTUM $.
      $( [17-Nov-2000] $)

    $( Associativity of sum of Hilbert space operators. $)
    hoaddassi $p |- ( ( R +op S ) +op T ) = ( R +op ( S +op T ) ) $=
