      VHOULACDFSULBCEFSUEUFULUMCABDEUGZFSMMUPPMMUQPVAUSVFLACDFTZBCEFTZULUPUQQRU
      HUIGUNURUMCVLFTUPUQVMVNUGUJUK $.
      $( [26-Nov-2000] $)

    $( Distributive law for Hilbert space operator difference. $)
    hocsubdiri $p |- ( ( R -op S ) o. T ) = ( ( R o. T ) -op ( S o. T ) ) $=
      ( vx chod co ccom cfv wceq chil wcel cmv wf hodval mp3an12 hocoi hocofi
      cv wral ffvelrni syl opreq12d eqtr4d hosubcli 3eqtr4d rgen hoeqi mpbi ) G
      UAZABHIZCJZKZULACJZBCJZHIZKZLZGMUBUNURLUTGMULMNZULCKZUMKZULUPKZULUQKZOIZU
